S.FORM: Joseph Kabila ryax sa tay 4 nqu tay 6, Joseph Kabila, squliq na sezi'. (minhtuw sa kawas tay 1971) mrhuw The Democratic Republic of the Congo ta' misuw hya' ga Joseph Kabila, aring ryax tay 26 squ byacing tay 1 sa kawas 2001 lga, musa' spazyang balay ms'rux kya la. Qnxan nya Joseph Kabila ga, la'iy ni Laurent Désiré Kabila. Olive Lembe di Sita ga, kneril ni Joseph Kabila. Joseph Kabila maki tay kawas 2006 msqun ki Olive Lembe di Sita ga, tehuk misuw qani.
